<div class="lg:p-8">
  <h1
    class="mt-20 font-header text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl lg:mt-32 lg:text-5xl"
    id="about_us"
  >
    Explore Dev Projects
  </h1>

  <p class="mb-16 mt-10 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-2xl">
    Are you ready to build? Here are some of the projects
    where Bitshala Fellows have contributed before and where
    new contributors are always welcome.
  </p>

